			<div class="content" id="post-content-4808587">
									

<p>This keeps coming up &#8212; the core of this article isn't that &quot;gotcha! Chaz is a cannibal!&quot; &#8212; this is apparent because we make it almost painfully obvious by July &#8212; it's the comedy inherent from seeing this guy go completely loony in the context. It's a comedy article &#8212; fresh narratives are fun bases for comedy but the core always will, and should be, the jokes. If the jokes didn't land for you, then that's just how it goes I guess.</p>
<p>In restaurant terms, I think you ate a salad expecting a steak.</p>

